<h1>About</h1>
<p>
<img alt="Gary Bishop." class="alignright tilt shadow" width="180" src="http://www.cs.unc.edu/~gb/media/gb.png" /> I am a Professor of <a href="http://www.cs.unc.edu/">Computer Science</a> at the <a href="http://www.unc.edu/">University of North Carolina</a> at Chapel Hill. My students and I develop software designed to enable people with disabilities to participate fully in education, literacy and play.
</p>

